ria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"119\" height=\"110\" src=\"https:\/\/shinertechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/church-2.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-110\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:340px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"165\" height=\"45\" src=\"https:\/\/shinertechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/iq-designs_PNG.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-113\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:302px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"154\" height=\"91\" src=\"https:\/\/shinertechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Petique_PNG.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-114\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-layout-grid-column wp-block-jetpack-layout-grid__padding-none\">\n<p><em>\u201cMike Hoar led mBank\u2019s networked computer systems, telephone and teleconferencing systems, and surveillance security systems through significant growth as a result of multiple complex bank acquisitions from 2014-2018.&nbsp; He was also instrumental in developing and maintaining the bank\u2019s Cybersecurity defense profile.&nbsp; I personally know him to be a very knowledgeable and capable IT professional with a strong sense of ownership and great pride in his work.&nbsp; I would recommend Mike Hoar and his services to any client who values performance, reliability, and security in their business technical systems and he will be a trusted partner\u201d.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>\u200b<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Kelly George<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>President &amp; CEO<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>mBank<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><em><br>\u201cMike Hoar has been invaluable to our church in the installation and operation of our computer\/multi-media system.&nbsp; His professional skill and experience make him a great asset to the ministry.&nbsp; Mike&#8217;s prompt response and skill make him a pleasure to do business with and I highly recommend him.&#8221;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>\u200b<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Paul Varoni<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Pastor&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Hiawatha Country Church<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><em>\u201cAs the owner of a growing company, I rely on technology that is cost-effective and reliable.&nbsp; Mike Hoar at SineTech provides exactly that for IQ Designs.&nbsp; He recently installed our new FortiVoice telephone system, upgraded our wireless network, and implemented a VPN so I can access our data wherever I travel in the world.&nbsp; Mike is knowledgeable, professional, and his work is excellent.&nbsp; I recommend his products and services to anyone who needs professional IT support for their business.\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>\u200b<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Robert Giles<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>CEO<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>IQ Designs, Inc.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-layout-grid alignfull column1-desktop-grid__span-9 column1-desktop-grid__row-1 column2-desktop-grid__span-3 column2-desktop-grid__start-10 column2-desktop-grid__row-1 column1-tablet-grid__span-4 column1-tablet-grid__row-1 column2-tablet-grid__span-4 column2-tablet-grid__start-5 column2-tablet-grid__row-1 column1-mobile-grid__span-4 column1-mobile-grid__row-1 column2-mobile-grid__span-4 column2-mobile-grid__ro